1
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:40,820
=Visage and Soul=

2
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:43,040
("The Unique Her"
Trilogy on Women's Relationships)

3
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:47,640
=Episode 23=

4
00:00:49,240 --> 00:00:50,040
What?

5
00:00:50,440 --> 00:00:51,960
You're really Ye Xiaoduo?

6
00:00:55,040 --> 00:00:55,640
Yifei,

7
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:57,720
about that jacket...

8
00:00:58,440 --> 00:01:00,720
You washed it
and wanted to return it to me.

9
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:02,800
But you were afraid
that Qiao Xiaomi would find out.

10
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:06,320
So you hid it in the parcel box
outside my house.

11
00:01:07,240 --> 00:01:09,280
There was even a note inside the pocket.

12
00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:12,000
And on it, you wrote, "Thank you".

13
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:14,200
Ye Xiaoduo.

14
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:15,400
It really is you.

15
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:17,400
But

16
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:20,400
why do you look like Qiao Xiaomi?

17
00:01:25,600 --> 00:01:26,720
The doctor said

18
00:01:28,880 --> 00:01:31,120
the chances of me
recovering my memory were very low.

19
00:01:32,360 --> 00:01:33,360
So,

20
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:37,080
my father had me
undergo facial reconstruction.

21
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:40,320
Maybe he thought

22
00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:42,440
it was better
for both of us this way.

23
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:46,240
How could he be so selfish?

24
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:49,920
He's already gone.

25
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,280
What's the point of blaming him?

26
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:55,280
I'm sorry.

27
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,880
For the way I treated you before.

28
00:01:57,920 --> 00:02:01,040
I'll pay for all the wrong I've done.

29
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:03,520
Yifei,

30
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:05,160
it's all in the past now.

31
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:13,560
Xiaomi...

32
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:14,520
No.

33
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:15,720
Xiaoduo.

34
00:02:15,720 --> 00:02:16,840
You're so brave.

35
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:18,680
Don't worry.

36
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:20,480
I know what I need to do.

37
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:24,080
Thank you, Yifei.

38
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:34,360
What did he ever do to you

39
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,440
for you to be this hard on him?

40
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,880
I heard you're getting married soon.

41
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:38,960
I just gave him

42
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,680
a little lesson.

43
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:42,400
He needs to learn

44
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,560
what's acceptable

45
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,800
and what's not

46
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,440
in the Qiao family.

47
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,160
Getting married?

48
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:51,080
To him?

49
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:53,080
That liar?

50
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:57,000
Right now, I could kill him.

51
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,320
By the way,

52
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:04,080
I remember everything now.

53
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,360
About who I am

54
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,520
and who he is.

55
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:11,680
And how good you've
always been to me.

56
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:22,240
If you hadn't warned me back then,

57
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:26,240
and helped me catch
those two cheaters,

58
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:29,200
I'd probably

59
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:31,000
still being fooled by them.

60
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:33,960
Xiaomi,

61
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:37,160
you finally remember
everything I've done for you.

62
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,280
I won't let anyone bully you.

63
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:43,800
You're not allowed

64
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,640
to see that liar Qin Yu ever again.

65
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:46,720
Do you hear me?

66
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,760
Dad's only looking out for you.

67
00:03:52,760 --> 00:03:53,520
Mind your own business.

68
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:54,320
Stop right there!

69
00:03:55,920 --> 00:03:58,000
Dad gave Ye Xiaoduo
a herbal clinic.

70
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:58,880
Did you know that?

71
00:03:58,880 --> 00:04:00,000
Why should I care?

72
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:02,360
Then what about the fact
that your boyfriend Qin Yu

73
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:04,400
and Ye Xiaoduo have been
getting cozy at that clinic?

74
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:05,720
Does that concern you?

75
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:09,080
What are you talking about?

76
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,720
My silly little sister.

77
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:14,880
Dad and I have known
about it for a long time.

78
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:16,720
You're the only one
who's been kept in the dark.

79
00:04:16,960 --> 00:04:18,600
If you know something, say it!

80
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:22,040
Go see for yourself.

81
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,760
Just prepare yourself.

82
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,600
Don't say I didn't warn you.

83
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:28,480
Give me the address.

84
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,360
Nice.

85
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,480
There's always drama to watch.

86
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:41,440
Hello.

87
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:43,000
Is Xiaomi here?

88
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,280
Who?

89
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,600
Qiao Xiaomi.

90
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,640
There's no one here by that name.

91
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:50,680
Sorry.

92
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:51,680
Wait.

93
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:54,880
Please tell Qiao Xiaomi

94
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:57,360
that I'm done
with the Qiao family.

95
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:59,320
And if she comes after me again,

96
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:00,440
I won't let her get away with it.

97
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:07,400
Do you have
a misunderstanding about Xiaomi?

98
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,600
Did she do something bad?

99
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:12,360
Who exactly are you to her?

100
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:15,200
I...

101
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:16,360
I'm her...

102
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:20,240
So this is your type now?

103
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,760
That's what you're into these days?

104
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,400
No.

105
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,600
And you, the illegitimate daughter.

106
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,920
Just like your mother,

107
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:30,120
always trying to steal
other people's men, huh?

108
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,640
Xiaomi.

109
00:05:32,640 --> 00:05:33,080
Are you okay?

110
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:33,880
Get away from me!

111
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:37,640
My dad was right.

112
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:40,720
I never should've gotten
involved with trash like you.

113
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:41,960
What are you talking about?

114
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:45,120
I'm saying you're trash.

115
00:05:45,840 --> 00:05:47,360
How did you become like this?

116
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:51,320
I get it now.

117
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:53,160
She's your girlfriend, isn't she?

118
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,840
Do you see
who she really is now?

119
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:56,680
You finally get it, don't you?

120
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:00,680
B*stard child.

121
00:06:01,280 --> 00:06:02,400
Believe it or not, I'll burn

122
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:04,400
this lousy herbal clinic to the ground!

123
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:05,200
Qiao Xiaomi!

124
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:07,520
The world doesn't revolve around you!

125
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:08,760
Get out of my way!

126
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:11,600
Do you realize
what happens if you do this?

127
00:06:11,840 --> 00:06:12,760
I'd like to see

128
00:06:13,080 --> 00:06:14,400
what could possibly happen.

129
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:19,160
Xiaomi,

130
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,240
calm down.

131
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:21,880
What are you doing?

132
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:22,520
Stay away from me!

133
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:23,200
Xiaomi!

134
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:24,880
Xiaomi!

135
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,520
Everyone, calm down!

136
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:34,080
But there's still
one thing I want to ask.

137
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:36,880
You were standing outside that day.

138
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:40,360
Why didn't you do anything?

139
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,440
Xiaomi!

140
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:47,080
Is anyone there?

141
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:48,400
Is anyone there?

142
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:49,360
Help!

143
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,240
Help!

144
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:52,800
Help!

145
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:53,960
Xiaomi!

146
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:54,920
Xiaomi!

147
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,880
Is anyone there?

148
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:57,720
Help!

149
00:06:59,280 --> 00:07:00,000
Help!

150
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,840
Is anyone there?

151
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:06,000
Help!

152
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:12,560
Isn't this better?

153
00:07:13,760 --> 00:07:15,560
That illegitimate girl is dead.

154
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,880
You're still alive.

155
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:22,280
You should cherish the life you've got.

156
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:28,960
You think I'm still the old Qiao Xiaomi?

157
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:31,600
The one you could kill so easily?

158
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:35,280
Enough talk.

159
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:38,760
Give me what I want.

160
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:40,720
Or you're not leaving here.

161
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,560
What are you so cocky about?

162
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,640
You're the one who's dead now.

163
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:49,320
Try me.

164
00:08:06,760 --> 00:08:08,680
Give it to me.

165
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:13,400
You don't actually think
you can threaten me

166
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:14,280
with this liar, do you?

167
00:08:14,280 --> 00:08:15,680
You've got to be kidding.

168
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:19,480
We've been brother and sister
for over 20 years.

169
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:21,560
Drop the act.

170
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:24,280
Give it to me!

171
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:26,160
Enough talking. Do it.

172
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:29,760
I'll count to three.

173
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:32,120
Three.

174
00:08:33,040 --> 00:08:33,800
Two.

175
00:08:35,560 --> 00:08:36,200
One.

176
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,200
Wait!

177
00:08:38,361 --> 00:08:41,360
(Share Transfer Agreement)

178
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,920
If you hadn't fought me for it,

179
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,240
I wouldn't have had to

180
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,880
set you up to start that fire.

181
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:54,160
If Dad had been
half as sensible as you,

182
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:56,000
he wouldn't have died so early.

183
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:59,440
Don't tell me Dad's death
was your doing too.

184
00:08:59,640 --> 00:09:00,640
Not exactly.

185
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,880
But when he was lying
in that hospital bed

186
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:04,320
begging me to save him,

187
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,600
I ignored him.

188
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:10,200
You monster.

189
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:12,600
Doesn't matter anymore.

190
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,440
Everything belongs to me now.

191
00:09:19,560 --> 00:09:20,800
You got all that recorded, right?

192
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:21,760
Got it all.

193
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,120
Qiao Xiaomi,

194
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,560
what are you trying to do?

195
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,560
So once again, we need your help

196
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:31,920
to use his mindset

197
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:33,160
to guide him into telling the truth.

198
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:37,840
I'm sorry, Xiaoduo.

199
00:09:38,560 --> 00:09:40,040
As a psychologist,

200
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:42,320
I've done so many things that hurt you.

201
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:45,840
It's okay, Chen Yue.

202
00:09:46,800 --> 00:09:48,520
The person who truly did wrong

203
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:49,840
is the one who should apologize.

204
00:09:54,880 --> 00:09:55,640
Alright.

205
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:57,040
I'll help you.

206
00:09:58,280 --> 00:09:59,600
Which means

207
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,680
Qiao Zhiwei,

208
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,320
you're finished.

209
00:10:31,736 --> 00:10:33,806
♪We say good morning, we say good night♪

210
00:10:33,806 --> 00:10:37,226
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

211
00:10:38,826 --> 00:10:40,716
♪The sweeter it is, the luckier we seem♪

212
00:10:40,716 --> 00:10:44,706
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

213
00:10:45,946 --> 00:10:47,806
♪Let me go, set me free♪

214
00:10:47,806 --> 00:10:51,846
♪Let me drown in reckless silence♪

215
00:10:52,386 --> 00:10:57,796
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

216
00:10:59,146 --> 00:11:01,286
♪The freedom you gave me♪

217
00:11:01,286 --> 00:11:04,926
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

218
00:11:06,186 --> 00:11:08,456
♪Love can barely move forward♪

219
00:11:08,456 --> 00:11:12,236
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

220
00:11:13,336 --> 00:11:15,576
♪The closeness I long for♪

221
00:11:15,576 --> 00:11:19,966
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

222
00:11:20,376 --> 00:11:22,196
♪I don't want to break free♪

223
00:11:22,196 --> 00:11:27,566
♪Take back the chains
disguised as freedom♪

